<translation id="1383876407941801731">Leita</translation>
<translation id="1566281227936819866">Sรฝnir vistaรฐa greiรฐslumรกta</translation>
<translation id="1717486229951421299">Listi yfir innskrรกningarupplรฝsingar sem eru fรฆrรฐar inn viรฐ snertingu opinn รญ hรกlfri hรฆรฐ.</translation>
<translation id="207576718733492531">Listi yfir innskrรกningarupplรฝsingar sem eru fรฆrรฐar inn viรฐ snertingu er lokaรฐur.</translation>
<translation id="2610239185026711824">Leggja til aรฐgangsorรฐ</translation>
