<translation id="2803478378562657435">Sรฝnir vistuรฐ aรฐgangsorรฐ og valkosti fyrir aรฐgangsorรฐ</translation>
<translation id="2903493209154104877">Heimilisfรถng</translation>
<translation id="3399357656427473483">Listi yfir innskrรกningarupplรฝsingar sem eru fรฆrรฐar inn viรฐ snertingu.</translation>
<translation id="3688051737190211318">Ef รพรบ treystir <ph name="ORIGIN" /> geturรฐu notaรฐ vistaรฐ aรฐgangsorรฐ til aรฐ skrรก รพig inn</translation>
<translation id="4631649115723685955">Fjรกrvildarkerfi tengt</translation>
<translation id="4660011489602794167">Sรฝna lyklaborรฐ</translation>
<translation id="4694050069269396220">Ef รพรบ treystir <ph name="ORIGIN" /> geturรฐu notaรฐ vistaรฐ aรฐgangsorรฐ fyrir annaรฐ vefsvรฆรฐi.</translation>
<translation id="5016175294846053194">Tillรถgur um sjรกlfvirka รบtfyllingu eru fyrir ofan lyklaborรฐiรฐ</translation>
<translation id="5088366526685584589">Sรฝnir vistuรฐ heimilisfรถng</translation>
